{
  "stem": "3380.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we only answer question to the United State, what they ask us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't tell it that she was sick of tuberculose, or she-- she's still in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I-- you know, I could have a different address.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we came to the United State.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was worry about, you know, that-- that we were-- in Germany, I know this is not the place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the United States, maybe I will be able to have help.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We came here in September-- in October the 13.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "On January the 5th, my son, Jack, was born in Mount Sinai Hospital, a handsome, beautiful boy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we came-- we took Jack to the doctor, what advised us not to have any-- any children, because-- [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Dr. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Berman. ?] And he said, if you were lucky once, don't try it again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If somebody jumps from the third floor and doesn't break his legs, he--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That doesn't mean that he should do it again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we show him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, this is our grandpa, we used to tell him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was an elderly man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He actually gave her the quinine through the-- in through the stomach, into the intestine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this actually subdued the heat-- the temperature.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she start feeling great.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we came to the United State.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She wasn't sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was not a-- a healthy woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you know, she brought three kids in this world, three lovely kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, she was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was expecting a baby.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have seen-- this is a place of opportunity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I start working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got-- through the HIAS, I got a job in the tannery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I worked here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I made $60 a week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a lots of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
